                        button.btn.btn-link(type='button' data-toggle='collapse' data-target='#collapseGeneralOne' aria-expanded='true' aria-controls='collapseGeneralOne')
                            | Question 1: Why should I choose you
                    i.fas.fa-angle-down.float-right
                #collapseGeneralOne.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingOne' data-parent='#accordionExample')
                    .card-body
                        | We specifically tailor our features to match student's desires to benefit them the best we can and what better way can we do this; giving you an interest free overdraft, a free Â£100 once you sign up, and a set interest rate of 2% on your savings account. We also have great customer service which will walk you through anything you need as we know this maybe your first bank your signing up to.
            .card
                #headingTwo.card-header
                    h2.mb-0
                        button.btn.btn-link.collapsed(type='button' data-toggle='collapse' data-target='#collapseGeneralTwo' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseGeneralTwo')
                            | Question 2: Am i automatically opting into online banking if I sign up
                    i.fas.fa-angle-down.float-right
                #collapseGeneralTwo.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingTwo' data-parent='#accordionExample')
                    .card-body
