            .card
                #headingThree.card-header
                    h2.mb-0
                        button.btn.btn-link.collapsed(type='button' data-toggle='collapse' data-target='#collapseGeneralThree' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseGeneralThree')
                            | Question 3: Is the bank safe
                    i.fas.fa-angle-down.float-right
                #collapseGeneralThree.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingThree' data-parent='#accordionExample')
                    .card-body
                        | We encrypt and decrypt everything such as transfers and account details to prevent any third parties getting hold of your data. We do our best to protect your data as only we have the key to decrypt your data
