                    .card-body
                        | You will have to directly contact us to speak whether or not you need an increase in overdraft by providing your parents' salary details
            .card
                #headingTwo.card-header
                    h2.mb-0
                        button.btn.btn-link.collapsed(type='button' data-toggle='collapse' data-target='#collapseAccountTwo' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseAccountTwo')
                            | Question 2: Why should your security be trusted
                    i.fas.fa-angle-down.float-right
                #collapseAccountTwo.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingTwo' data-parent='#accordionExample')
                    .card-body
